		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Yaztromo">Yaztromo</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Yaztromo">( 655250 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64193640">		
		on Saturday January 27, 2024 @11:01PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23207468&amp;cid=64193640">#64193640</a>)
		<small><a href="http://web.me.com/yaztromo" title="http://web.me.com/yaztromo" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
<a href="//slashdot.org/~Yaztromo/journal/" title="Wednesday May 20, 2009 @03:30PM" class="user_journal_display">Journal</a> </small>
