	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64195996"><p>quote, "But I use MacOS because I like unix and I don't like windows and I do like having a nice desktop experience."</p><p>I used Mac OS X for many years because I hated Unix (almost as much as Windows) and the Mac did a good job of hiding Unix from me.</p><p>Now I use Mint Cinnamon, which likewise does a pretty good job of hiding Linux's Unix-like traits. And it's a desktop OS that still works like a desktop OS, not trying to mimic a phone or a tablet.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64195996">

</div>
